API Documentation

The interactive documentation driven by the OpenAPI for the Human Services Data API (HSDA). All GET API paths are publicly available, where the POST, PUT, and DELETE require an appid and appkey. This is just meant to be a demo application showing what is possible with any HSDA implementation in support of Open 211 efforts.
